user.biography: The Official Instagram from Jeffrey Herlings. 🇳🇱 3 times MX2 Worldchampion "12 "13 "16 1 time MXGP Worldchampion "18 ♛♛♛♛ 94 GP wins. Red-Bull KTM.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jeffrey Herlings on September 19, 2021. May be an image of dirt bike, motorcycle and outdoors.

node.text:
Where can I start about today? Amazing day for me and the team. 1 - 1 for P1 🏆🥇 Riola Sardo you was good for us. 🇮🇹
Making it GP win nr. 94 aswell what puts me 2nd on the all time winners list. 🔥✅
@ktmfactoryracing @redbull @oakleymotorsports @jumbo @giampishow @milwaukeetool @hennekenskay @hsf_logistics @knmv_motorbond @debrug.eu @iamspecialized @autoridderhof #josmaas
📸@jpacevedophoto

node.text:
Turning 27 today. 🥳🎉🎁
Damnit... I am getting old. 😫
Another year older and grayer and wiser.
